<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idd2b192f6-4ef6-11f1-9110-db228fde61c5" identifier="/us/usc/t47/s767"><num value="767">§ 767.</num><heading> Methods to pursue privatization</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The President shall secure the pro-competitive privatizations required by this subchapter in a manner that meets the criteria in part B.</p>
